OLED IP Display for Raspberry Pi
A simple Raspberry Pi project that shows the Pi’s local IP address on a small OLED display.

OLED Pin	Raspberry Pi		GPIO Number
VCC	           3.3V     		   1
SCL	           GPIO 3 (SCL)            3
SDA	           GPIO 2 (SDA)            5
GND	           GND                     6

